Web or within any organization.

Some supported blogging sites include:
  • SharePoint blog
  • WordPress
  • Blogger
  • Windows Live Spaces
  • Community Server
  • TypePad


You will be prompted to register your blog account if this is firt time you have a published blog.
You may add additional blog accounts or change existing blog account at any time.

Microsoft Active Accessibility
In Q1 2011 Telerik UI for WinForms implement MSAA support which makes them the first suite to support the latest standarts in UI automation and accessibility.

RadWizard
In Q1 2011 Telerik UI for WinForms provides the RadWizard - a brand new control with wide range of customization and navigation options which makes creating installers and wizards easier than ever.

Extended Right-to-Left and localization support
In Q1 2011 Telerik UI for WinForms extend their possibility of localization and Right-to-Left languages support.

RadTreeView
RadTreeView is significantly improved in Q1 2011 making it up to 10 times faster than before. Check boxes, radio buttons, editors and a lot more customization options are provided as well.
